overview: Divinidylle Tour is the third live album by singer Vanessa Paradis. The album was recorded during her Divinidylle Tour and was also released with a DVD which documented the tour and Paradis' promotion of the album. The DVD won a Victoires de la Musique award for Best DVD Musical of the year.  From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
title: Vanessa Paradis: Divinidylle Tour
